{"tid":567736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直播解車公籤　何君堯：叫青年行妥路　勿搞港獨、自決","createTime":"2018-02-21T06:46:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T15:55:47.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2c893b0dd1339ab3bc5e7522e19528e2a8f94bc3","tid":567736,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180221/s00001/2357671dc12588ce7dcc52b7a393bff9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180221%2Fs00001%2F2357671dc12588ce7dcc52b7a393bff9.jpg&h=1b0a05c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上周六（17日）大年初二，鄉議局主席劉業強按傳統到沙田車公廟為香港求籤，並求得中籤。立法會議員何君堯認為，應用平常心看待籤文。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯昨晚於facebook直播中直言，「求籤，求神不如求自己，最緊要自己努力」，形容籤文放諸四海皆準，「不辛苦不努力，何來有收穫？」他特別提到23條立法，稱「無論早晚，應該要做就要做&hellip;&hellip;治亂世要用重典」。<br />\n<br />\n何君堯又說，籤文鼓勵青年人要努力向前勿怕困難，「行條路要準及妥善，肯定不是搞亂事，推翻香港，搞獨立港獨、自決」，強調「這些路必定是死路一條」，「不能搞港獨，不能搞歹毒，不能夠冷血。撇除這些，無論點樣行條路，一定是成功。就算失敗都好，最後都是歸你成功。如果行錯條路，懸崖跌落去就粉身碎骨架喇」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180221/s00001/1519188608959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180221%2Fs00001%2F1519188608959&d=K1AVKCpQm38pRxEEHM3wugIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=3123aa73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180221%2Fs00001%2F1519188608959&h=770fbf97\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180221/s00001/1519188608959</a>"},{"pid":"8adb202806d5ecbec790001b13e9404de2757d42","tid":567736,"uid":38143,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"基督徒解籤文要落地獄"},{"pid":"612811d3a205add4bbbc4cb5ef31c90e65779709","tid":567736,"uid":131064,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:49:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>何妖，率眾狗吠人</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2b6e81671218be74897eb6650a15674e82f063bc","tid":567736,"uid":168506,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:52:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd6e6fa7257e80ed3c53a0ad429d29775fbbc1a4","tid":567736,"uid":11001,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8adb202806d5ecbec790001b13e9404de2757d42","tid":567736,"uid":38143,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"基督徒解籤文要落地獄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T07:49:07.000Z","msg":"地獄同地府，不用分得哪麼細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718fa71ef2413bee9ba933a7c5f0d965b063b682","tid":567736,"uid":137999,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"佢亂咁解真係唔怕有報應？"},{"pid":"bd2dcd090d34b384e7b176a76a3246f61f6e3c98","tid":567736,"uid":63482,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T13:05:55.000Z","msg":"典型靠古惑上位既人"},{"pid":"14672f77391891459585e1028cfe5046eee13670","tid":567736,"uid":162424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:26:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be234db7a8decc41d9a03710810d93f069f1be32","tid":567736,"uid":126283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"718fa71ef2413bee9ba933a7c5f0d965b063b682","tid":567736,"uid":137999,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T07:54:22.000Z","msg":"佢亂咁解真係唔怕有報應？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"死完老母唔夠想死埋其他親友掛"},{"pid":"ce3baeb30a654072d965319bde4f0229e92885f3","tid":567736,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:55:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點睇都係叫港獨要勇往直前, 起步難, 但先苦後甜喎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n車公靈簽 第四十一簽：中簽<br />\n<br />\n簽文：攝衣欲過灘頭淺，轉計回來怕濕身；人若不信辛苦事，何能取得保全寧。<br />\n<br />\n解簽：凡事小心，自身平吉，求財吉利<br />\n<br />\n斷簽：家宅後吉，家宅不寧，佔病苦口良葯，自身艱辛，出入小心，婚姻不合，求財無，隻求收獲，不願耕耘，罪過，欲上天堂，吃喝玩樂，<br />\n<br />\n家宅：先苦後甜<br />\n<br />\n出行：合宜<br />\n<br />\n姻緣：退縮則不成<br />\n<br />\n行人：途中有阻<br />\n<br />\n生育：不順但無礙<br />\n<br />\n訴訟：和談可解決<br />\n<br />\n事業：起步難<br />\n<br />\n搬遷：不宜<br />\n<br />\n自身：要勇敢果斷<br />\n<br />\n疾病：可痊愈<br />\n<br />\n財運：可有財運"}]}